<DATE>
<P>
March 20, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
TV Times; Page 7; Television Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
557 words 
</P>
