</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Two Westside students have been named finalists in the sixth annual Music 
Center Spotlight Awards. 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles residents Ryan Smith and Alpin Seung-Hi Hong will perform March 29 
during the final competition. 
</P>
