<P>
VALLEY HOME SALES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Sales of existing single-family homes in the San Fernando Valley withstood the 
Northridge earthquake, rising 18.8% during February compared to 1993, the San 
Fernando Valley Assn. of Realtors has reported. 
</P>
