<P>
PREP ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In the Canyon Relays boys' swimming meet: 
</P>
<P>
 Villa Park wins -- The Spartans won three of the eight relays and finished 
with 104 points, topping second-place Santa Margarita, which had 90 points. 
</P>
<P>
 In the Canyon Relays girls' swimming meet: 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Margarita wins -- The Eagles won six of eight relays and scored 116 
points. Villa Park, which won the other two relays, was second with 104 points. 
</P>
<P>
 In the Laguna Hills boys' volleyball tournament: 
</P>
<P>
 Los Amigos 2, El Modena 1 -- Kiet Tran had 25 kills for Los Amigos (3-0) as 
the Lobos won the championship with an 8-15, 15-3, 15-4 victory. Tran was named 
tournament MVP. 
</P>
