<P>
 Quick recovery: NCAA probation often seems a mere annoyance, rather than 
devastation to a basketball program.On probation in recent years, Illinois, 
Kentucky, Maryland, Missouri and Syracuse recovered quickly enough to play in 
the NCAA tournament this weekend. 
</P>
<P>
 Maybe it's the company: Word is that there was much grousing on the New York 
Yankee bus from Sarasota, Fla., back to their spring base at Ft. Lauderdale 
after a game against the Chicago White Sox. Word is that it might have been 
because owner George Steinbrenner was aboard. JIM HODGES 
