the 24-hour period ending at 6 p.m. Saturday. Oct. 1 is the beginning of the 
official rain year. 04,22,15,14,17 Rainfall Rainfall Normal rainfall Location 
last 24 hours since Oct. 1 to date Camarillo 0.39 7.61 11.02 Casitas Dam 0.28 
