<HEADLINE>
<P>
ARTS HIGH SCHOOL HOLDING AUDITIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Auditions are being scheduled for students in grades 9 to 11 who want to 
enroll this fall in the Los Angeles County High School for the Arts. 
</P>
<P>
 Visual arts portfolio screenings and auditions in dance, theater, vocal and 
instrumental music will be held at 9 a.m. at Cal State Los Angeles on April 17. 
</P>
<P>
 Students at Arts High School, which is tuition-free, also take a full range of 
academic courses and may participate in the school's college-credit program. 
</P>
<P>
 To receive an application and set an audition appointment, students may call 
(213) 343-ARTS. The application deadline is March 25. 
</P>
<P>
 Spanish-speaking parents and students may obtain more information by calling 
(213) 343-2565. 
</P>
