 * 
</P>
<P>
 "I Love L.A." by Randy Newman (1983) 
</P>
<P>
 Written by Randy Newman 
</P>
<P>
 "Victory Boulevard (We love it)" 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
